HEADWORD: Blueback
<hw>Blue"back`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>A trout (<spn>Salmo oquassa</spn>) inhabiting some of
the lakes of Maine.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>A salmon (<spn>Oncorhynchus
nerka</spn>) of the Columbia River and northward.</def> <sd>(c)</sd>
<def>An American river herring (<spn>Clupea ⟦ae⟧stivalis</spn>), closely
allied to the alewife.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

